{"tid":1265479,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"五千萬守升旗禮","createTime":"2019-06-29T08:02:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-29T08:05:02.000Z","uid":67412,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"3cb56bf2485bb0e0c518e05cfd1013b7301f0147","tid":1265479,"uid":67412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T08:02:27.000Z","msg":"政府修訂《逃犯條例》風波持續，面對網民號召臨近七一發起示威行動，警方高度重視布防準備，其中盛傳成為示威者包圍目標的金紫荊廣場將會屯駐重兵防守。據消息人士估計，準備的警力規模至少如6月9日、6月12日立法會外衝突事件相若，將會派出近5000警力駐守。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n至於規模方面，警方將派出Tier 1、Tier 2及Tier 3部隊，其中Tier 1為現機動部隊及衝鋒隊，以及快速應變部隊；Tier2為軍裝警務人員，同時有駐守機動部隊及衝鋒隊經驗。消息續指，至於新購入的護目鏡相信亦會登場，優先讓Tier 1及2人員配備。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190629/bkn-20190629130936805-0629_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190629%2Fbkn-20190629130936805-0629_00822_001.html&d=FYZ0PdCaIZeH%2BWUkJYSmq5BhszO9bAnYmyMPTpIehd8%3D&h=6a941a8c\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190629/bkn-20190629130936805-0629_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"d7e397fb86d86f1627bc4fa0709ef22a49f842d9","tid":1265479,"uid":67412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T08:04:43.000Z","msg":"寫錯字sorry!係五千警"},{"pid":"94acd99418551e97f102917e8bb602ed82d95eb5","tid":1265479,"uid":253586,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T08:05:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kiNpD8L.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkiNpD8L.png&h=395afc1b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n突然!6月30晚立法會煲底集結!不要去灣仔送頭!<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1265427\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1265427</a>"}]}